    <narrativeNotes>Trolly Curling was selected to be deployed to a distant Rimworld as part of a colonisation attempt, but disappeared before the pods launched. In truth, Trolly fell into the backrooms, and another rejected colonist stole Trolly's indentity and position on the Rimworld. Aging, but vengeful, Trolly turned to dark Archotechs for power, and eventually joined a colony of other backrooms denizens, finally having a safe city to begin her practice of necromancy and lichdom.</narrativeNotes>
